oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Thesaurus Transcriptions: Part 2
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This recording features songs on Hank Snow's album "The Thesaurus Transcriptions." This is part two of fifteen tapes for this album. This tape is the sixteenth of an unidentified number of tapes.
